{"tid":1841603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「緊急」醫護人員全部同我入嚟 唯一出路","createTime":"2020-01-25T10:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:51:54.000Z","uid":141607,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"83c920471a34c8356b57d8c9c70633deca0e51d7","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"首先多謝你哋喺呢個星期入面無私嘅付出，用你哋專業嘅知識同埋堅守崗位，繼續去醫治身邊嘅人。<br />\n但係而家嘅情況根本就唔係為香港嘅病人去服務，大量生活係重災區嘅蝗蟲過晒來香港，你哋醫治嘅去到而家仲係唔係香港人，再加上政府根本就冇諗過去協助你哋呢班前線嘅醫護人員。<br />\n2003年嘅沙士，我仲係幼稚園，坦白講我對沙市毫無印象。我知道嘅就只係政府嘅無能將一班熱血有心嘅救護人員，就咁推咗佢哋去死。前車可鑑 你哋仲願意為而家嘅香港、甚至係嗰班嘅蝗蟲去擺上生命？<br />\n我希望醫護人員真係可以鼓起勇氣去罷工，而當你地罷工嘅時候，各行各業嘅市民都同樣會去罷工。對唔住，好似將你哋推上一個好重要嘅位置，但係唯有你哋先係呢件事嘅重點人物<br />\n所以無論如何，我希望所有嘅醫護人員係初五各行各業啟市嘅一日發起冇了期嘅罷工，咁先可以將而家件事嘅迫切性話俾政府聽(雖然佢都唔會聽)，以及發起攬炒嘅計劃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>初五 29號 醫護罷工</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"003d9782d43f6f70878c134395cd5bee227068c6","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>初五 29號 醫護罷工</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3a03a8ab1255e71d5c6a0a53fe3e214910f08c84","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>初五 29號 醫護罷工</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e68393068908d03e3271c59ea96ae7436a6eb96d","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:18:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>初五 29號 醫護罷工</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3e71cb0957faa0d8c52ddca2d41303e34435d0ee","tid":1841603,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"[全民罷工] 究竟封關有幾唔科學？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1841533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1841533</a>"},{"pid":"a5778a2f77a3d06c3c8bee1874133bf18a52fdfb","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"仲未封鎖 你救嘅只不過係一班不得好死嘅蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>初五 29號 醫護罷工</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2a4a217d2989bbc91ce45a63a2d7c4e49d2bf17d","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:21:33.000Z","msg":"鼓起勇氣踏出第一步啦 我哋所有人會同你喺度<br />\n大量嘅工會都會同你一齊並肩而行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>初五 29號 醫護罷工</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"673d01fe79c6e86f9d8996e048f5c8514ecafd63","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"要嚟香港嘅大陸人都嚟哂啦"},{"pid":"d063d507f0644877378ef9e8172f7dc553098b3c","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GaJB6C8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaJB6C8.png&h=5f9898e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"769ccf3e544217f864d8613d5a8d16c193cdc5d7","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"673d01fe79c6e86f9d8996e048f5c8514ecafd63","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"要嚟香港嘅大陸人都嚟哂啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:26:59.000Z","msg":"到而家都仲未封關 意味着嘅就只有蝗蟲仲可以嚟香港 多一個已經好多"},{"pid":"6cc8c6205464aad3bda72adb6d2ea285e7a1481a","tid":1841603,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"有無任何集會可以去？<br />\n無做HA的小EN想幫忙湊人數"},{"pid":"aceb5972c67b3a0c0ba6bcb3e6bb7010ccc1db2d","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769ccf3e544217f864d8613d5