020-01-25T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"已經太遲，你係防大陸人"},{"pid":"fa515960de87ac433ee5a0c798e0ca3e3d1a5223","tid":1841603,"uid":79680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5JiAy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5JiAy9.png&h=fe60e6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[推上去] 罷工比返工救得更多嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eba1d888c59991b006628ef4d39fa3aa62637497","tid":1841603,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"220951a00e4467c9a26aced2b254d1092505c239","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb0814a1312b78a59ded9f5f86b1d30c9786aa1","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36c592359f480aadf5dfa5cd86e577ef2913805","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3baecea7fd0960c6022121211ddb4c5f36d6acba","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;4日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"好多行業都係初四之後先開爐 所以初五正式罷工不成問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"已經太遲，你係防大陸人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"防嘅唔止係大陸人 仲有班夠膽死返大陸嘅人"},{"pid":"08353d800b595d1657c459c877823093ec93e2f3","tid":1841603,"uid":230001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99f0d3a5ff9cc2bf3eb75ef8d12122ed933dafd","tid":1841603,"uid":235119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"55746cadb9e5ef356cd50919e240cf53bcbbca3f","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"220951a00e4467c9a26aced2b254d1092505c239","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb0814a1312b78a59ded9f5f86b1d30c9786aa1","tid":1841603,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36c592359f480aadf5dfa5cd86e577ef2913805","tid":1841603,"uid":141607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"好多行業都係初四之後先開爐 所以初五正式罷工不成問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"已經太遲，你係防大陸人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"防嘅唔止係大陸人 仲有班夠膽死返大陸嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"所以重29號？到有醫護個口罩被班on9拉落嚟，有on9大鬧醫院，某程度上佢哋有份造成"},{"pid":"9574e203cfa651b8173acb53353f007ff4357d1a","tid":1841603,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:45:10.000Z","msg":"6天蓋出「火神山醫院」不夠用！武漢決定旁邊再蓋一所「雷神山」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669737.jpg&h=1816b700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲為了再6天內蓋出「火神山醫院」，大陸調動上百台挖土機整地。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n記者蔡紹堅／綜合報導<br />\n武漢市防疫指揮部23日決定參照SARS期間7天建成的「小湯山醫院」，在6天內興建一所武漢肺炎的專門醫院，定名為「火神山醫院」。不過，似乎是考量到「火神山」的床位有限，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午決定，要在2月5日前在「火神山」旁再建一所「雷神山醫院」。<br />\n「火神山醫院」的承建單位中建三局人員透露，火神山醫院的面積為2.5萬平方公尺，可容納1000張床，規劃在6天內建成，也就是說會在2月1日完工，2月3日投入使用。<br />\n<strong>▼挖土機通宵趕工，為了達成6天蓋出醫院的目標。（圖／新華網）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669734.jpg&h=9699b0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了達成6天完工的目標，中建三局23日晚上就展開動作，調集上百台挖土機、推土機等施工機械抵達工地，通宵進行場平、回填等施工。主體的施工則從25日開始，整個施工期間，項目部將按照兩班倒的方式日夜不停施工，高峰期將有1500名建設者和280台套施工機械設備同時奮戰。<br />\n不過，似乎是考量到「火神山醫院」的1000個床位不夠用，武漢市防疫指揮部25日下午3點半舉行調度會，決定在「火神山醫院」旁邊，在2月5日前再建成一所「雷神山醫院」，新增床位1300張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4669/d4669716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4669%2Fd4669716.jpg&h=fa4a9f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，多名醫護也遭感染。（圖／武漢中心醫院）</strong>"},{"pid":"a07305a829af11a59bf1e92fb60085528763e162","tid":1841603,"uid":12439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"仲要等29號,真係保你大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}